A clue nest (elite) is randomly obtained from Woodcutting or bird house trapping on Fossil Island. Searching the nest will give players an elite clue scroll and a bird nest.

All clue nests except beginner clue nests are dropped instead of logs.

The ring of wealth (i) doubles the rate of clue nest drops above beginner from Woodcutting in the Wilderness.
